FBIS3-22093 "jptdd013__l94096" JPRS-tdd-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 21 March 1994 WEST EUROPE ITALY Large Heroin Seizure Reported in Trieste NC2103203894 London Kanal-6 Television in Turkish 1600 GMT 21 Mar 94 NC2103203894 London Kanal-6 Television Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Text] Some 300 kg of heroin was seized in a Turkish truck in Trieste in northern Italy. Its market price is $294 million. It was reported that this record amount of narcotic material was destined for Austria, Italy, Germany, and the Netherlands, and that two people have been detained in connection with the incident. It was found out that the truck was brought to the Trieste port on the "Kaptan Abidin Doran" ferry. It was learned that the ferry belongs to Maritime Transportation.
